{"tid":1125885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"體操港將邱沚峯美國受傷半癱 病情惡化出現炎症發燒","createTime":"2019-04-26T04:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T17:39:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"096b36b5a5edddbe69aeec86ca1ade370500c5c6","tid":1125885,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】現年29歲的本港體操運動員邱沚峯（Jesher），上月在美國練習期間，落地一刻發生意外，頸椎及脊髓受傷，胸部以下癱瘓。他現時在美國接受治療，其Facebook專頁今日透露，邱沚峯近日情況惡化，出現發炎及發燒等感染徵狀。<br />\n為邱沚峯眾籌的網站Facebook專頁「Pray for Jesher Tsz Fung Yau」上月公布邱沚峯已轉送復康醫院，不幸近日邱沚峯病情惡化，據網站最新帖文指，他近日出現炎症及發燒。 不少網民紛紛留言為他打氣並捐款。<br />\n由於醫療費高昂，友人為他發動眾籌，目標是籌40萬美元。據眾籌網址所示，現時邱沚峯已籌得27.2萬美元，距離40萬美元目標已達逾一半。<br />\n根據網上記錄，邱沚峯由2010年開始連續3屆參加「全港競技體操公開及新秀比賽」的公開組賽事，先後兩度奪得跳馬冠軍，以及一次男子自由體操冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R2ugXbFusdzJ5A4peCrKsA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190425a203340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FR2ugXbFusdzJ5A4peCrKsA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190425a203340.jpg&h=fd5f24e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片：Facebook專頁「Pray for Jesher Tsz Fung Yau」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%94%E6%93%8D%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%87%E9%82%B1%E6%B2%9A%E5%B3%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E5%8D%8A%E7%99%B1-%E7%97%85%E6%83%85%E6%83%A1%E5%8C%96%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%82%8E%E7%97%87%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92-123200317.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2593%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2582%25B1%25E6%25B2%259A%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%258D%258A%25E7%2599%25B1-%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2587%2592